data.description: Fully renovated in 2016 3/2 + converted garage on a Supersize 12000 sqft lot near Lake Houston. Renovations included New Roof, Windows in 2016, 16 seer Carrier AC in 2016, All Flooring (ceramic,laminate & carpet) in 2016, all doors & frames, trim work, granite counter-tops(kitchen&baths), toilets, tub & shower, light fixtures & fans, exterior siding, painted inside and out, all new electrical service box,interior outlets & switches, sinks, disposal, sink fixtures, and the pool was complete resurfaced in 2016.
